headline: GE HealthCare Announces Advanced Imaging Innovations for OEC 3D C-arm to Help Improve Precision Care in Practice of Interventional Pulmonology
summary: CHICAGO, November 22, 2024--GE HealthCare announces additional clinical applications now available as part of the OEC 3D mobile CBCT C-arm portfolio.
